title: Harrier hound joins biosecurity frontline (Ministry for Primary Industries of New Zealand)
text: ( Source : Ministry for Primary Industries of New Zealand ) She looks like a giant beagle. She isn't, but she is the first harrier hound to work for the Ministry for Primary Industries as a biosecurity detector dog. Lou lou and her handler
